===Noun===
'''moegoe'''
#(South African) [[pejorative]]: An [[idiot]]. A [[dolt]]. A [[mampara]]. 
:The sense is of somebody who is really [[dumb]].
#*"There are so many people who made it to my '''Moegoe''' of the Week list but unfortunately I can only select one. I was looking for a stronger word than ''''Moegoe'''' .... At one point I was considering a word they use in South Africa, 'Mampara', but that was also not strong enough. I then had to settle for '''Moegoe'''."
